## FaceBook Download Scraper.

- Author : [Vihanga-YT](https://github.com/vihangayt0)

***

## Example Downloader 1. [fdown.net]
```js
const { 
fbdl1,
fbdl2
} = require('vihangayt-fbdl')

let res = await fbdl1('https://www.facebook.com/ngakakocak/videos/video-lucu-dan-gokil/607085686836013')
console.log(res)
```

## Example Downloader 2. [getfvid.com]
```js
const { 
fbdl1,
fbdl2
} = require('vihangayt-fbdl')

let res = await fbdl2('https://www.facebook.com/ngakakocak/videos/video-lucu-dan-gokil/607085686836013')
console.log(res)
```
